@startuml
left to right direction
title YompYomp Use Case Diagram

actor "Guest User" as Guest

' This is someone who has already set up and saved their profile
actor "Profiled User" as Profiled

actor "Users" as Users
actor "Weather API" as Weather
actor "Map API" as Map_

Users <|-up- Guest
Users <|-up- Profiled


rectangle "YompYomp App System" {
  Users --> (Complete Profile Quiz)

  Profiled -down-> (Log Trip)
  (Log Trip) <.left. (Rate Trip) : <<extend>>
  Profiled --> (View Personalised Recommended Trails)

  Guest --> (View General Recommended Trails)

  Users --> (View All Trails)
  Users --> (Search Trails)

  Users --> (Add Missing Trail)
  Users --> (Modify Existing Trail)

  (View All Trails) ..> (View Single Trail) : <<include>>
  (View General Recommended Trails) ..> (View Single Trail) : <<include>>
  (View Personalised Recommended Trails) ..> (View Single Trail) : <<include>>
  Map_ -up-> (View Single Trail)
  Weather -up-> (View Single Trail)
}
@enduml